00:00:48.360 --> 00:00:51.640
The key to a successful setup is to have your perches

00:00:51.641 --> 00:00:53.201
higher than your nest boxes.

00:00:53.202 --> 00:00:54.961
If they're not higher than your nest boxes,

00:00:54.962 --> 00:00:58.241
